     =========================================================
     Geant4 - an Object-Oriented Toolkit for Simulation in HEP
     =========================================================

                            Test01
                            ----------

  The purpose of this test is to exercise the CSG as well as boolean solids 
  extensively using the full apparatus of the G4 geometry.

  Author: Vladimir Grichine
  Contributors: Simone Giani, John Apostolakis

  To run it you can use

    g4test *.in or *.mac

 which will compile, run it and check its output, 
 or compile it and say:

 ./AIX-AFS/test01 < test01.in | tee test01.newout
 diff test01.out test01.newout

 to run it and check the output yourself.

    J. Apostolakis, July 5th, 1998
